      <title>零售商 Conn’s 因销售额下滑考虑申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/retailer-conn-s-mulls-bankruptcy-filing-amid-sales-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，家具零售商 Conn’s Inc. 正准备申请破产，因为它面临销售下滑，且难以整合竞争对手的连锁店。]]></description>
