      <title>世界银行启动担保额度增至 200 亿美元的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/world-bank-launches-program-to-boost-guarantees-by-20-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行启动了一项新计划，旨在到2020年将投资担保额提高到200亿美元，以调动数万亿美元的投资，为贫穷国家的发展和气候项目提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/world-bank-launches-program-to-boost-guarantees-by-20-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
